酒 女 金 ドラッグ
Alcohol, women, money, drugs...

418
00:29:28,040 --> 00:29:29,540
やっちゃってコンプラ
Breaking the compliance!

419
00:29:29,540 --> 00:29:31,040
Chillって aiight
Just chill, alright?

420
00:29:31,040 --> 00:29:33,540
冗談じゃんブラックジョーク
It's just a joke, a black joke!

421
00:29:33,540 --> 00:29:35,540
中指立てたくなるような事情
Reasons that make you want to raise your middle finger

422
00:29:35,540 --> 00:29:38,240
ありすぎて指が足りねえから
Are so many, I don't have enough fingers!

423
00:29:38,240 --> 00:29:40,040
Hands up and what's up

424
00:29:40,040 --> 00:29:41,540
最低？ もともとだろ
Terrible? I was like that from the start!

425
00:29:41,540 --> 00:29:43,040
Bring it on!

426
00:29:43,040 --> 00:29:45,540
「まあまあ」 なんかいらない
I don't need any "so-so" options!

427
00:29:45,540 --> 00:29:47,840
欲しがります死ぬまでは
I'll crave for more until I die!

428
00:29:47,840 --> 00:29:51,040
伸びた背丈 育った街に投げキッス
Blow a kiss to my taller height and the town I grew up in!

429
00:29:51,040 --> 00:29:54,040
見せ場はこっから 覚悟しとけよ
The highlight starts here, prepare yourself!

430
00:29:54,040 --> 00:29:56,540
ダッダッダ 僕ら大人になる
Da-da-da, we're growing up!

431
00:30:00,048 --> 00:30:03,548
そこのけそこのけ 街になびく 秘め騒ぐ心から
Get out of the way, get out of the way! Fluttering in the streets, from my secretly clamoring heart...

432
00:30:03,548 --> 00:30:05,048
覚悟しとけよ
You better prepare yourself!

433
00:30:05,048 --> 00:30:08,048
段々々 ほら 音に鳴る カウントダウン
Step by step, look, the sound rings out, the countdown...

434
00:30:08,048 --> 00:30:10,548
狙い 狙い 痛い 痛い 日々に
...aiming, aiming at these painful days.

435
00:30:10,548 --> 00:30:13,548
燦々と かます 仁義
Brilliantly serving up justice!

436
00:30:13,548 --> 00:30:16,548
誰も読めない 先も読めない これで勝負
No one can read it, the future is unreadable, this is the showdown!

437
00:30:16,548 --> 00:30:19,548
バグも マスも ドレも すべて
Even the bugs, the masses, whichever it is, take them all along...

438
00:30:19,548 --> 00:30:23,048
ツレて 満ちて 生きて 射ち抜いて 狂い咲きしよう
...and fill up, live, shoot through, let's bloom in madness!

439
00:30:23,048 --> 00:30:26,048
We've got a very special show! Let's go!

440
00:30:38,548 --> 00:30:41,048
かったるい 事はしない
I don't do tedious things.

441
00:30:41,048 --> 00:30:44,048
言葉が かげり ズレない
My words don't shadow or slip.

442
00:30:44,048 --> 00:30:46,548
解るか？ あたしの 美学
Do you understand my aesthetic?

443
00:30:46,548 --> 00:30:50,048
この 場で 正直な
Right here, my honest...

444
00:30:50,048 --> 00:30:53,048
拳 一つが
...single fist...

445
00:30:53,048 --> 00:30:56,548
切り札
...is my trump card!

446
00:30:56,548 --> 00:30:59,548
ガナる ラッタッタ
Shouting "rat-tat-tat"!

447
00:30:59,548 --> 00:31:02,548
一撃 で K.O. するならば
If it's a one-hit K.O., then...

448
00:31:02,548 --> 00:31:05,548
そら 行くぞ
Here we go!

449
00:31:08,048 --> 00:31:09,548
Ow!

450
00:31:09,548 --> 00:31:14,548
Alright, Otomos, and every single grem at home, put your hands up!

451
00:31:21,548 --> 00:31:23,048
こんな もんじゃない
This isn't all I've got!

452
00:31:23,048 --> 00:31:25,548
段々々 ほら 音に鳴る カウントダウン
Step by step, look, the sound rings out, the countdown...

453
00:31:25,548 --> 00:31:28,048
酸いも甘いも 見分けて今
...telling the sour from the sweet now.

454
00:31:28,048 --> 00:31:31,548
燦々 交わる 未来を
With no fear of...

455
00:31:31,548 --> 00:31:34,548
恐れることもないよ 解るでしょ<
...the brilliantly intersecting future, you understand, right?

456
00:31:34,548 --> 00:31:37,548
地平 線まで
All the way to the horizon...

457
00:31:37,548 --> 00:31:40,548
届かない
...where we can't reach,

458
00:31:40,548 --> 00:31:43,048
連れて行くよ
I'll take you with me,

459
00:31:43,048 --> 00:31:48,048
息を抜いて 頂戴な 頂戴な
so please, take a breath, please.

460
00:31:56,048 --> 00:32:00,048
それは皆々様、お先にバイバイっ！
Well then, everyone, bye-bye for now!

