467
00:32:19,048 --> 00:32:21,048
Oh my god. We have to do this. Write this down, write this down right now!

468
00:32:21,048 --> 00:32:23,048
Let's bring it to the suits! Yeah!

469
00:32:27,548 --> 00:32:29,548
Oh my god, they're gonna love this!

470
00:32:29,548 --> 00:32:31,048
They're gonna love it!

471
00:32:31,048 --> 00:32:34,548
They're gonna love us! They love us. They love us!

472
00:32:45,048 --> 00:32:51,048
This is bad.

473
00:32:51,548 --> 00:32:58,048
This is bad. (Slow-motion)

