Don- Never give up on your dreams.

476
00:33:07,548 --> 00:33:09,048
Really?

477
00:33:09,048 --> 00:33:14,048
Yeah. I feel like... you had half a good idea.

478
00:33:14,048 --> 00:33:17,548
And you had half a good idea, too.

479
00:33:17,548 --> 00:33:22,048
And together... That's a... We'll... ...whole good idea.

480
00:33:22,048 --> 00:33:26,048
